{"data":[{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Hai, ng\u00e0y 19/02/2018 05:30 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 19/2: HLV Conte \"l\u1eadt t\u1ea9y\" \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu Barcelona","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939808\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939808\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>HLV Conte ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Barcelona. </strong>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y,&nbsp;chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia Italia&nbsp;kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barcelona r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia t\u1ea1i Champions League.&nbsp;\"\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu khi kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng khai th\u00e1c tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 19/2: HLV Conte &amp;#34;l\u1eadt t\u1ea9y&amp;#34; \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu Barcelona - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-19/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-19-2-HLV-Conte-chi-ra-diem-yeu-lon-nhat-cua-Barcelona-c1-1518977069-326-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Conte</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sao tr\u1ebb Man City \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea5p r\u01b0\u1ee1i. </strong>Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Zinchenko m\u1edbi l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man City ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro Danilo. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u1edfng Zinchenko, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Man City \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u00e0nh cho anh m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi ngay c\u1ea3 khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u0169 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2021. Trong \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ukraine c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u1eeb 40 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 60 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barcelona&nbsp;m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n sau khi b\u00e1n Neymar.&nbsp;</strong>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Ter Stegen kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barcelona m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t \u0111i ng\u00f4i sao Neymar \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. \"D\u00f9 m\u1ea5t Neymar nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u00e2n binh gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t&nbsp;h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. Hy v\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi ch\u01a1i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Hazard l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real.&nbsp;</strong>Trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean t\u1edd Telefoot m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Hazard \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u201cTrong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra c\u1ea3. N\u0103m n\u00e0o h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real ho\u1eb7c PSG. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i CLB, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fabregas bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch khi\u1ebfn Barcelona ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.&nbsp;</strong>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng anh&nbsp;bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Barcelona.&nbsp;\u201c\u0110\u00e2y&nbsp;v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady, s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u1edf ph\u00eda sau. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, HLV Conte s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho thanh l\u00fd \u201dh\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n\u201d ki\u1ebfm 87 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-18/640mu-mou-1518972514-209-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho thanh l\u00fd \u201dh\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n\u201d ki\u1ebfm 87 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh tay thanh l\u1ecdc l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng th\u00eam ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch mua s\u1eafm.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-19-2-hlv-conte-lat-tay-diem-yeu-barcelona-c409a939808.html","id":"385"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Hai, ng\u00e0y 19/02/2018 00:04 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho thanh l\u00fd \"h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n\" ki\u1ebfm 87 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939794\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939794\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>PSG h\u1ecfi mua Rojo 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u1edd The Sun cho hay, Rojo \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 \u1ea2 r\u1eadp s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Old Trafford. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Rojo v\u1edbi MU ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho thanh l\u00fd &amp;#34;h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n&amp;#34; ki\u1ebfm 87 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-18/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Mourinho-thanh-ly-mu-rojo-1518972388-7-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Mourinho v\u00e0 Rojo</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Herrera \u0111\u1ebfn Milan, MU c\u00f3 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AC Milan \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 h\u1ecfi mua Ander Herrera. Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia cho hay, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ebfn MU. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Mourinho. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho t\u00e2n binh Matic v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arsenal h\u1ecfi Luke Shaw, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 khi c\u00f3 th\u00eam Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Aubameyang. H\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, HLV Wenger mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Luke Shaw \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a \"Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0\" nh\u01b0ng MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n r\u1ebb. Daily Star cho hay, HLV Mourinho ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Shaw ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ee7 mua m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi thay th\u1ebf.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Griezmann kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00ec Sanchez</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sanchez k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 Griezmann. T\u1edd Don Balon cho hay, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Old Trafford khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Sanchez khi\u1ebfn anh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y. Griezmann v\u00e0 Sanchez c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Atletico s\u1ebd \"h\u1ea1 c\u00e1nh\" xu\u1ed1ng Barca.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fellaini ch\u1ecdn xong b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fellaini l\u1ea1i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i n\u00ean MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi ngay t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Mirror cho hay, Fellaini quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sang Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00f3c x\u00f9 l\u00e0 Besiktas.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU: Pogba b\u1ecb nghi kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Real, Mourinho ph\u1edbt l\u1edd\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-18/640x480-1518920275-635-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU: Pogba b\u1ecb nghi kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Real, Mourinho ph\u1edbt l\u1edd</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>MU th\u1eafng Huddersfield trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y Paul Pogba ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-mourinho-thanh-ly-hang-ton-kiem-87-trieu-bang-c409a939794.html","id":"384"},{"date":"Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, ng\u00e0y 18/02/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 18/2: Carrick ch\u1ec9 ra truy\u1ec1n nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1i MU","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939669\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939669\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Carrick ch\u1ec9 ra truy\u1ec1n nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1i MU</strong><strong>.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Michael Carrick ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho MU \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam bao l\u00e2u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf m\u00ecnh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 Carrick \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi trong ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Scott McTominay: \u201cScott l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o. McTominay c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.\u201d</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 18/2: Carrick ch\u1ec9 ra truy\u1ec1n nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1i MU - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-18/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-18-2-Carrick-chi-ra-truyen-nhan-tai-MU-mu3-1518899893-347-width660height367.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Scott McTominay</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>D\u00e0n sao Liverpool sang T\u00e2y Ban Nha x\u1ea3 h\u01a1i.&nbsp;</strong>Do kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi FA Cup, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n&nbsp;Liverpool quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sang T\u00e2y Ban Nha kho\u1ea3ng 4 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edfng \u00e1nh n\u1eafng \u1ea5m \u00e1p n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y. Chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i x\u1ea3 tr\u1ea1i sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Porto \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u1ea5t.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" ch\u1ec9 ra nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Chelsea.&nbsp;</strong>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng khi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Chelsea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Chelsea kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft HLV Conte c\u00f3 theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh hay kh\u00f4ng. Ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ed3i quay l\u1ea1i gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Xabi Alonso ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean tam t\u1ea5u Liverpool.&nbsp;</strong>C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i hoa ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen b\u1ed9 ba h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Mohamed Salah, Roberto Firmino v\u00e0 Sadio Mane c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. \"Th\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc khi t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd v\u00ec c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 ba \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Jurgen Klopp, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Dortmund.\u201d</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barca g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Eibar.&nbsp;</strong>D\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Eibar l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c c\u0169ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Eibar \u0111\u1ea9y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 khi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 cao. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\".</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Huddersfield Town - MU: Uy l\u1ef1c kinh h\u1ed3n, c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-18/mu2-1518896932-726-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Huddersfield Town - MU: Uy l\u1ef1c kinh h\u1ed3n, c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>M\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-18-2-carrick-chi-ra-truyen-nhan-tai-mu-c409a939669.html","id":"383"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y, ng\u00e0y 17/02/2018 00:09 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 17/2: Pep vu\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u HLV hay nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939535\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939535\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Pep vu\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u \u201cHLV hay nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng\u201d:</strong> C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, BTC Premier League v\u1eeba c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a danh hi\u1ec7u HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 1/2018, v\u00e0 Eddie Howe \u2013 \u201cthuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d c\u1ee7a Bournemouth l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a, Pep Guardiola kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 5 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 17/2: Pep vu\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u HLV hay nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-16/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-17-2-Pep-vuot-danh-hieu-skysports-howe-eddie-bournemouth_4232670-1518799918-520-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Eddie Howe ch\u1eb7n chu\u1ed7i 4 th\u00e1ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng \"HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League\" c\u1ee7a Pep</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2017, tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Bournemouth nh\u1ea3y v\u1ecdt l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 10. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Eddie Howe kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0o v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh&nbsp; chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng m\u00e0n \u201ch\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t\u201d nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Chelsea 3-0 ngay tr\u00ean Stamford Bridge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tottenham s\u1eafp \u201ctr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n\u201d Pochettino: </strong>K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Tottenham v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014, Mauricio Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London th\u00e0nh th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c \u1edf Premier League, \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u201c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn\u201d kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi thi \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League (v\u1eeba l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Juventus tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch). \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00ed do khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid l\u1eabn PSG \u0111\u1ec1u ra s\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, BL\u0110 \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u201ctr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n\u201d Pochettino d\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Real nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef t\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t: </strong>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Real Madrid cho hay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Toni Kroos \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi PSG \u1edf Champions League (th\u1eafng 3-1), d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kho\u1ea3ng 2 tu\u1ea7n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i th\u00eam 3-4 tr\u1eadn n\u1eefa, kh\u00f4ng k\u1ec3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real Betis cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y (c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo g\u1ed3m Leganes, Deportivo Alaves, Espanyol, and Getafe).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D\u00f9 v\u1eady Kroos ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League (v\u00e0o 7/3).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u201cC\u00e1ch ng\u0103n Messi t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0\u2026 t\u00f9y c\u01a1 \u1ee9ng bi\u1ebfn\u201d</strong>: \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Deco, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u1ea3 Chelsea l\u1eabn Barca tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i thu\u1ed9c khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League. Theo c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 40 tu\u1ed5i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0o ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Lionel Messi ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u201ct\u00f9y c\u01a1 \u1ee9ng bi\u1ebfn\u201d b\u1edfi ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd l\u00e0m g\u00ec.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Liverpool chu\u1ea9n mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c: </strong>Mirror \u0111\u01b0a tin, CLB Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c AS Roma nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson. N\u1ebfu v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n\u201d s\u1ed1 1 \u0110T Brazil s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Ederson (35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1eeb Benfica sang Man City m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2017) \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0103n \u0111\u1ee9t La Liga c\u00f3 Real &amp; Barca\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-07/1517953038-411-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0103n \u0111\u1ee9t La Liga c\u00f3 Real &amp; Barca</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>S\u1ee9c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean La Liga.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-17-2-pep-vuot-danh-hieu-hlv-hay-nhat-thang-c409a939535.html","id":"382"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ng\u00e0y 16/02/2018 03:14 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 16/2: Mourinho g\u1eedi \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u MU \"l\u00e0m l\u00e0nh\" Conte","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939407\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939407\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Mourinho b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eedi qu\u00e0 \"l\u00e0m l\u00e0nh\" Conte: </strong>M\u1ed9t ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd chen ngang&nbsp;bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u00e0 Hull City thu\u1ed9c khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 FA Cup, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi g\u1eedi cho&nbsp;HLV Antonio Conte chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a... MU in t\u00ean chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1. \u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i h\u01a1n, chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00ed c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho&nbsp;- ng\u01b0\u1eddi gh\u00e9t cay gh\u00e9t \u0111\u1eafng, nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n&nbsp;\"kh\u1ea9u chi\u1ebfn\"&nbsp;n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda v\u1edbi Conte \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 16/2: Mourinho g\u1eedi \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u MU &amp;#34;l\u00e0m l\u00e0nh&amp;#34; Conte - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-16/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-16-2-Mourinho-gui-qua-493e42c100000578-5395731-pranksters_have_handed_an-1518719000-645-width660height338.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Conte \"\u0111\u1ee9ng h\u00ecnh\" khi nam di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean h\u00e0i Le Lene \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ed1t ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean g\u1eedi t\u1eb7ng Conte chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u MU in t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u1eef k\u00ed c\u1ee7a \"k\u1ebb th\u00f9\" Jose Mourinho</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><div style=\"text-align: center;width: 100%;clear: both;position: relative;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<div style=\"position:relative;max-width: 660px;margin: 0 auto\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 16/2: Mourinho g\u1eedi \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u MU &amp;#34;l\u00e0m l\u00e0nh&amp;#34; Conte - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-16/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-16-2-Mourinho-gui-qua-mou-conte-780x405-1518719000-595-width660height343.jpg\" />\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image\" style=\"position: absolute;display: block;overflow: hidden;width: 660px;height: 90px;color: white;bottom: 0px;left: 0px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"24h-banner-in-image-close\" style=\"top:5px;right: 5px;position: absolute;display: none;overflow: hidden;width: 22px;height: 22px;color: #ccc;font-size: large;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 16/2: Mourinho g\u1eedi \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u MU &amp;#34;l\u00e0m l\u00e0nh&amp;#34; Conte - 3\" onclick=\"in_image_close();\" id=\"in-image-close\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\"></img>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n                \r\n            </div></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, tay di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean c\u0169ng \"g\u00e0i b\u1eaby\" th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mourinho</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"Mourinho g\u1eedi m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 n\u00e0y cho \u00f4ng v\u1edbi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn: G\u1eedi Antonio v\u00ec t\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n l\u00e2u b\u1ec1n\", tr\u00edch l\u1eddi tay ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean, tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean h\u00e0i n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Le Lene.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh ng\u1eb7t ngh\u00e8o, Conte t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ed1i r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng k\u1ecbp \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i h\u00f3m h\u1ec9nh: \"C\u1ee9 gi\u1eef chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y n\u00f3 sau bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o\",</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\u0110\u00e1 Europa League, Mkhitaryan ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1... 77: </strong>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/16 Europa League gi\u1eefa Arsenal v\u00e0&nbsp;\u00d6stersunds FK,&nbsp;Henrikh Mkhitaryan b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ed1 77, thay v\u00ec s\u1ed1 7 quen thu\u1ed9c. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, lu\u1eadt UEFA quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00ed m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00e1o cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i&nbsp;c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, trong khi s\u1ed1 7 \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1&nbsp;Alexis Sanchez - c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u1ec3n sang MU - trong su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Barca \u0111\u1ea5u&nbsp;Chelsea, Pique th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng: </strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 Chelsea t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i thu\u1ed9c khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League , trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\"Nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t \u1edf La Liga v\u00e0 c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ef1 tin cao \u0111\u1ed9, tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ee7 quan. M\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Champions League c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed5 s\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 bi\u1ec3n\", tr\u00edch l\u1eddi Pique.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>\"Dele Alli c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u00e1n ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8\"</strong>: Tr\u00ean t\u1ea1p ch\u00ed GQ, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tottenham -&nbsp;Jermaine Jenas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e0n em Dele Alli l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \"kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf\", th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London n\u00ean c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc b\u00e1n ngay \u1edf k\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1. Hi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a MU, Real, Barca.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong khi \u0111\u00f3,&nbsp;Jenas c\u0169ng khuy\u00ean&nbsp;Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \"G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\" trong 1-2 n\u0103m n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Liverpool nh\u1eafm c\u1ef1u sao Real thay Coutinho:</strong> Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb t\u1edd Bild, CLB Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez v\u00e0o k\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p thay th\u1ebf&nbsp;Philippe Coutinho - ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba chuy\u1ec3n sang Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 145 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>James Rodriguez kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayer Munich v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2017 theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 2 n\u0103m t\u1eeb Real tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1&nbsp;10,6 tri\u1ec7u euro. Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35,3 tri\u1ec7u euro sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"PSG c\u00f3 Neymar v\u1eabn kh\u1edd d\u1ea1i C\u00fap C1: C\u1ea7n Mourinho \u0111\u1ec3 x\u01b0ng b\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-15/640psg2-1518648285-543-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">PSG c\u00f3 Neymar v\u1eabn kh\u1edd d\u1ea1i C\u00fap C1: C\u1ea7n Mourinho \u0111\u1ec3 x\u01b0ng b\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>PSG v\u00e0 Neymar v\u1eabn qu\u00e1 non n\u1edbt khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-16-2-mourinho-gui-ao-dau-mu-lam-lanh-conte-c409a939407.html","id":"381"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 15/02/2018 02:30 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 15/2: MU kh\u1ed5 luy\u1ec7n ch\u1edd ph\u1ee5c h\u1eadn \u201cb\u00e9 h\u1ea1t ti\u00eau\u201d","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939243\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939243\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><em>Video MU t\u1eebng thua \u0111au 1-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town \u1edf v\u00f2ng 9 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y:</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mourinho b\u1eaft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU kh\u1ed5 luy\u1ec7n ch\u1edd tr\u1ea3 n\u1ee3 \u201cb\u00e9 h\u1ea1t ti\u00eau\u201d: </strong>\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 5 FA Cup v\u00e0o 0h30 ng\u00e0y 18/2 (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam) t\u1edbi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town, \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong m\u01b0a l\u1ea1nh h\u00f4m qua \u1edf Carrington.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 15/2: MU kh\u1ed5 luy\u1ec7n ch\u1edd ph\u1ee5c h\u1eadn \u201cb\u00e9 h\u1ea1t ti\u00eau\u201d - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-15/Tin-HOT-bong-da-15-2-MU-kho-luyen-cho-phuc-han-be-hat-tieu-4934be0300000578-0-image-a-10_1518614966837-1518633058-569-width660height466.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-style: italic;\">Sanchez (ph\u1ea3i) v\u00e0 Matic tr\u00f9m m\u1eb7t k\u00edn m\u00edt t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n gi\u1eefa tr\u1eddi m\u01b0a l\u1ea1nh c\u00f9ng MU \u1edf trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Carrington</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C\u00f2n nh\u1edb, h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, c\u0169ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n John Smith\u2019s, <strong>MU</strong> t\u1eebng thua s\u1ed1c 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 c\u1ee7a HLV David Wagner v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c h\u1eadn c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mkhitaryan l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh \u1edf Europa League:</strong> Sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Arsenal thua Tottenham 0-1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 27 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, t\u00e2n binh Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Arsene Wenger r\u1ea5t m\u1ef1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Armenia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d sang Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ea5u Ostersunds v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng 16/2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/16 Europa League. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Mkhitaryan ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 gi\u00fap MU v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Kane c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Gerrard \u1edf Champions League:</strong> V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ghi 1 b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Tottenham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u1eeba qua \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League n\u0103m nay, Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111u\u1ed5i k\u1ecbp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 Stephen Gerrard (Liverpool) m\u00f9a 2008/09 v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 7 b\u00e0n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ghi b\u00e0n si\u00eau t\u1ed1c s\u1ed1 1 cho Juve, Higuain v\u1eabn b\u1ecb fan \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 l\u0103ng m\u1ea1:</strong> \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tottenham v\u1eeba qua, Gonzalo Higuain v\u1edbi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho Juventus ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n nhanh nh\u1ea5t cho \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin\u201d t\u1ea1i Champions League.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D\u00f9 sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n n\u1eefa t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh c\u1ef1u sao Real \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 Tottenham g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c tifosi c\u1ee7a Juve ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bayern ch\u1ed1t xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai James Rodriguez: </strong>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m x\u1ee9 Bavaria\u201d s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a anh th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. H\u00e8 2017, Bayern \u0111\u00e3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n James Rodriguez t\u1eeb Real v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"zone_banner_sponser_product\">\r\n                            \r\n                        </div>\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u201dSi\u00eau c\u00f2\u201d t\u1eb7ng Mourinho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-15/640mu-icardi-1518628433-603-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \u201dSi\u00eau c\u00f2\u201d t\u1eb7ng Mourinho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Theo Corriere Dello Sport, Mino Raiola \u0111ang th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Icardi v\u1ec1 MU.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-15-2-mu-kho-luyen-cho-phuc-han-be-hat-tieu-c409a939243.html","id":"380"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 N\u0103m, ng\u00e0y 15/02/2018 00:15 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: \"Si\u00eau c\u00f2\" t\u1eb7ng Mourinho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939239\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939239\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>\"Si\u00eau c\u00f2\" t\u1eb7ng Icardi cho Mourinho</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o \"si\u00eau c\u00f2\" Mino Raiola. \u00d4ng b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ph\u00ed hoa h\u1ed3ng cao b\u1edfi tay \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00e0y \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Mino Raiola \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1c th\u00e0nh Ibrahimovic, Pogba, Lukaku v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: &amp;#34;Si\u00eau c\u00f2&amp;#34; t\u1eb7ng Mourinho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-15/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-mu-icardi-1518628305-42-width660height371.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Mauro Icardi l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Inter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo tin t\u1eeb Corriere Dello Sport, Mino Raiola \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Mauro Icardi \u0111\u1ebfn MU. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 ghi 18 b\u00e0n cho Inter m\u00f9a n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2021. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, MU ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i chi ra kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Paul Pogba v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed1c 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i, Umtiti ra y\u00eau s\u00e1ch v\u1edbi Barca</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Barca nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Umtiti kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng. T\u1edd Don Balon cho hay, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp ph\u1ea3i t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean 103.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, ngang b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u00e0 MU \u0111\u01b0a ra. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bartomeu t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 Umtiti khi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 m\u1edf c\u1eeda.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Herrera li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi AC Milan</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ander Herrera kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Mourinho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. T\u1edd Tuttosport ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Herrera s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan ngay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i k\u1ebft th\u00fac. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Serie A s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 MU 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alderweireld</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Alderweireld t\u1ea1i Tottenham kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafc. Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 18 th\u00e1ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n. V\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn Turin ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Juventus. Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alderweireld. Manchester Evening News cho hay, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 \u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1eebng 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU 661 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u201cv\u1ee9t \u0111i\u201d: Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i 1 t\u1ef7 b\u1ea3ng t\u1eadu 5 SAO Real\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-14/mu3-1518587066-83-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU 661 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u201cv\u1ee9t \u0111i\u201d: Mourinho \u0111\u00f2i 1 t\u1ef7 b\u1ea3ng t\u1eadu 5 SAO Real</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-sieu-co-tang-mourinho-tien-dao-100-trieu-bang-c409a939239.html","id":"379"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 T\u01b0, ng\u00e0y 14/02/2018 04:47 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 14/2: Arsenal \u201c\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf HLV Wenger","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939085\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939085\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Arsenal \u201c\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf HLV Wenger. </strong>Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a London Evening Standard, Arsenal d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh s\u1ebd \u201cthuy\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c\u201d cho HLV Arsene Wenger n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc London ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i top 4. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d \u0111ang b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf Champions League m\u00f9a sau. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, BL\u0110 Arsenal s\u1ebd thay \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d b\u1eb1ng Massimiliano Allegri - nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i Juventus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 14/2: Arsenal \u201c\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf HLV Wenger - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-13/Tin-HOT-bong-da-Arsenal-an-dinh-nguoi-thay-the-HLV-Wenger-sport-preview-massimiliano-allegri-to-arsenal-660-1518541010-298-width660height440.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Allegri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd thay HLV Wenger t\u1ea1i Arsenal</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chelsea ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba cu\u1ed9c th\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t.</strong> Do n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Theo t\u1edd Telegraph, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Thibaut Courtois, Eden Hazard hay N\u2019Golo Kante, cho d\u00f9 Real hay PSG c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Coutinho kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi r\u1eddi Liverpool. </strong>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Philippe Coutinho gia nh\u1eadp Barcelona t\u1eeb Liverpool trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng. V\u00ec l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham gia lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn knock-out Champions League, d\u00f9 t\u1eebng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u00fap Liverpool l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Coutinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed3i ti\u1ebfc khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gary Neville v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV.</strong> Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Sky Sports, c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n MU, Gary Neville th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ngo\u00e0i th\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ecba. Sau khi gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 n\u0103m 2011, Neville t\u1eebng c\u00f3 4 n\u0103m l\u00e0m tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Valencia. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ea3 hai l\u1ea7n Gary Neville v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>N\u1ebfu Bayern kh\u00f4ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C1, Lewandowski s\u1ebd ra \u0111i.</strong> T\u1edd Bild cho hay, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Lewandowski s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Allianz Arena v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU 661 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng: Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft th\u1ee9 3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, khuynh \u0111\u1ea3o Cup C1\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-13/bail-640x480-1518469187-110-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU 661 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng: Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eaft th\u1ee9 3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, khuynh \u0111\u1ea3o Cup C1</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>T\u1eeb g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, MU x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-14-2-arsenal-an-dinh-nguoi-thay-the-hlv-wenger-c409a939085.html","id":"378"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 T\u01b0, ng\u00e0y 14/02/2018 00:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho t\u1eadu c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 120 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-939086\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-939086\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Mourinho t\u1eadu c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 120 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chris Smalling c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 c\u1ee7a MU tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Newcastle cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu an to\u00e0n. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Phil Jones c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\".</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: Mourinho t\u1eadu c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 120 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-13/Chuyen-nhuong-MU-Mourinho-tau-cap-trung-ve-120-trieu-bang-660mu-mourinho-1518540354-83-width660height465.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m Smalling v\u00e0 Jones</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HLV Mourinho c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a MU tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. Theo tin t\u1eeb Daily Mirror, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \"\u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng\" tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh De Gea.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Harry Maguire l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Leicester g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o m\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng pha l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Leicester s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Maguire d\u01b0\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Varane. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng Real c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e8o. Theo t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a Daily Mirror, MU s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra kho\u1ea3ng 120 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MU s\u1eafp b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 t\u00ean s\u00e2n Old Trafford</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>B\u00e1n t\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c khai th\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng m\u1edbi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady MU lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u00f2m ng\u00f3. T\u1edd The Sun ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, n\u1ebfu gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ean Old Trafford s\u1ebd thu v\u1ec1 26,2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. Con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 cao h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u Man City thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ean s\u00e2n th\u00e0nh Etihad (19,1 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a). Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" \u0111ang ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i r\u1ea5t d\u1eef d\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dani Alves kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay Valencia</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n MU s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Dani Alves \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Valencia b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang ph\u1ea3i, Manchester Everning News \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn. T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 MU c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Alves. Valencia v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Fosu-Mensah khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Arsenal \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mua Smalling</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Smalling li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi\u1ebfn MU \u00f4m h\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a HLV Wenger. T\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \"Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0\" \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh nh\u01b0ng MU kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e2m n\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0a Smalling v\u1ec1 Emirates trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"Alexis Sanchez kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5: Tho\u00e1t ki\u1ebfp \u201dg\u00e1nh\u201d Arsenal, l\u1ea1i lo \u201dg\u00e1nh\u201d MU\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-13/sdfasdfsafsadfsadfsd-1518511995-844-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">Alexis Sanchez kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5: Tho\u00e1t ki\u1ebfp \u201dg\u00e1nh\u201d Arsenal, l\u1ea1i lo \u201dg\u00e1nh\u201d MU</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>MU \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o v\u1ebft xe \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Arsenal khi c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \"ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5\" Alexis Sanchez.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"chuyen-nhuong-mu-mourinho-tau-cap-trung-ve-120-trieu-bang-c409a939086.html","id":"377"},{"date":"Th\u1ee9 Ba, ng\u00e0y 13/02/2018 05:05 AM (GMT+7)","title":"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/2: Morata c\u00e3i l\u1eddi Conte, quy\u1ebft ch\u00ed tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i","type":"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n: \u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1","img_url":"","new_desc":"<h3>Tin n\u00f3ng</h3><div class=\"text-conent\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear padTB5\" style=\"float:left\">\r\n\t\t\t<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"width:auto !important\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>  \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-like.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" alt=\"\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>                  \t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/fb-share.png\" width=\"55\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right fb-count-409-938894\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style=\"padding-right:5px\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"http://static-us.24h.com.vn/images/2014/google-share.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"20\" style=\"vertical-align:middle\" /><span class=\"mxh-ver-left\"></span><span class=\"mxh-ver-right g-count-409-938894\"></span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n\t\t <p><strong>Morata c\u00e3i l\u1eddi Conte, quy\u1ebft ch\u00ed tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</strong> HLV Antonio Conte m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 Alvaro Morata ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng v\u1eeba m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Morata kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Chelsea.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><img class=\"news-image\" alt=\"Tin HOT b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/2: Morata c\u00e3i l\u1eddi Conte, quy\u1ebft ch\u00ed tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, '')\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-13/Tin-HOT-bong-da-sang-13-2-Morata-cai-loi-Conte-quyet-chi-tro-lai-gettyimages-852322698-1518461303-755-width660height495.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color:#0000ff;font-style:italic;text-align:center;\">Morata kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a HLV Conte</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tottenham nh\u1eadn hung tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Juventus. </strong>Trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Tottenham, Toby Alderweireld ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Juventus t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out Champions League. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb l\u00e2u, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Pochettino kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Alderweireld v\u00ec e ng\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Madrid m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Neymar.</strong> H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Marcelo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf \u0110T Brazil, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y c\u1eadu em Neymar s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn knock-out Champions League gi\u1eefa Real v\u00e0 PSG, Marcelo cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho Real Madid\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Abramovich quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Batshuayi.</strong> Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Hans-Joachim Watzke, Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Chelsea, Michy Batshuayi. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Chelsea, Roman Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Tottenham e s\u1ee3 Dybala.</strong> HLV Mauricio Pochettino c\u1ee7a Tottenham h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Paulo Dybala c\u1ee7a Juventus. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn knock-out Champions League, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cDybala l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. S\u1ebd r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 cho Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y khi Tottenham \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Juventus\u201d.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<img alt=\"MU thua s\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n: Mourinho b\u00e1n g\u1ea5p 4 SAO\" class=\"img_tin_lien_quan_trong_bai\" src=\"http://image-us.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2018/images/2018-02-12/mu8-1518448724-77-width640height480.jpg\" /></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"title-bv\">MU thua s\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n: Mourinho b\u00e1n g\u1ea5p 4 SAO</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"ct-bv\">\r\n<p>Sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU \u0111ang b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"see-now\">B\u1ea5m xem &gt;&gt;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\t\r\n\t</div>","new_url":"tin-hot-bong-da-sang-13-2-morata-cai-loi-conte-quyet-chi-tro-lai-c409a938894.html","id":"376"}]}